    <div class="content"><div class="editor-left-col">
<h2>Welcome to SCRI</h2>
<p>SCRI is a Scottish success story. We are the bridge between rural production and urban wellbeing. We have an unrivalled track record of delivering innovative knowledge, products and services that enrich the Scottish and UK economies.<br />
<br />
SCRI is active in 30 countries supporting sustainable development and the production of healthy, natural food. <a title="Link to the About Us page" href="http://www.scri.ac.uk/aboutus" target="_self">Learn more about SCRI</a>.</p>
<p><a href="news/newinstitute_updates" target="_self" title="Link to the New Institute updates page">Read about plans for Scotland's New Institute - <br />
The James Hutton Institute</a></p>
</div>
<div class="editor-right-col">
<h2>Photo of the Day</h2>
<span class="hide">DO NOT EDIT BELOW THIS POINT</span>  <div class="potd">  <div class="node">
        <h3 class="title"><a href="/image/arabidopsis">Arabidopsis</a></h2>    <!--<span class="submitted"></?php print $submitted?></span>
    <span class="taxonomy"></?php print $terms?></span>-->
    <div class="content"><a href="http://www.scri.ac.uk/image/arabidopsis"><img src="http://www.scri.ac.uk/files/images/arabidopsis.thumbnail.jpg" alt="Arabidopsis" title="Arabidopsis"  class="image image-thumbnail " width="250" height="250" /></a><p>Arabidopsis is a model species used in plant research. Read more <a title="Link to the flowering time page" target="_self" href="../research/genetics/genesanddevelopment/floweringtime">about this research</a>.</p>
</div>
    <div class="links"><ul class="links inline"><li class="first last comment_forbidden"><span class="comment_forbidden"><a href="/user/login?destination=comment/reply/750%2523comment_form">Login</a> or <a href="/user/register?destination=comment/reply/750%2523comment_form">register</a> to post comments</span></li>
</ul></div>  </div>
