<div id="programmes">
<h1>SCRI Research</h1>
<div class="editor-left-col"><a title="Read about our biodiversity research" href="research/biodiversity">
<h2>Biodiversity</h2>
</a>
<p class="text-left"><span class="image-right"><img height="74" width="90" alt="Image showing Scots pine trees" class="image-right" title="Image showing Scots pine trees" src="/scri/image/scotspine_thumb.jpg" /></span><br />
<br />
Preserving and utilising the variety of the world&rsquo;s species.</p>
<font size="2" face="Arial"><a title="Read about our sustainability research" href="research/sustainability">
<h2>Sustainability</h2>
</a></font>
<p class="text-left"><span class="image-right"><img height="74" width="90" alt="Image showing the Centre for Sustainable Cropping - Balruddery" class="image-right" title="Image showing the Centre for Sustainable Cropping - Balruddery" src="/scri/image/balruderry_thumb.jpg" /></span><br />
<br />
Designing arable systems for food security and a healthy environment.</p>
</div>
<div class="editor-right-col"><a title="Read about our climate change research" href="research/climatechange">
<h2>Climate Change</h2>
</a>
<p class="text-left"><span class="image-right"><img height="74" width="90" class="image-right" alt="Image of Scotland map showing temperature changes" title="Image of Scotland map showing temperature changes" src="/scri/image/climatechange_thumb.jpg" /></span><br />
<br />
Effective responses to the impacts of environmental change.</p>
<a title="Read about our research to make Scotland wealthier and healthier" href="research/healthier">
<h2>Wealthier and Healthier</h2>
</a>
<p class="text-left"><span class="image-right"><img height="74" width="90" alt="Image of Glen Fyne raspberries" class="image-right" title="Image of Glen Fyne raspberries" src="/scri/image/glenfyne_rasps_thumb.jpg" /></span><br />
<br />
Working to improve prosperity and health through better food.</p>
</div>
</div></div>
